title: Dell PowerVault ME5: Fans
agents: dell_powervault_me5
catalog: hw/storagehw/dell
license: GPLv2
distribution: Sher Zaman
description:
 Monitors the cooling fans of a Dell PowerVault ME5 enclosure, including health,
 status and speed. Fan speed is recorded as a metric; optional upper and lower
 levels on speed are available and off by default.

 State is taken from the fan health value reported by the array. Conditions are
 configurable via the "Dell PowerVault ME5 fan" ruleset.

item:
 The fan durable id (for example {"fan_0.0"}).

discovery:
 One service is created per fan that reports a speed.
